      "content": "i just cant stand being at this desk all day. it feels so insulting knowing that the real reason i'm stuck in this entry level role is to keep my involvement in the 2022 maritime trade accords under wraps. i know the documents i helped draft are being scrubbed of my specific phrasing to make it look like a generic committee decision, but i've seen the traces they missed. it's exhausting having to pretend i'm just some regular guy when i'm actually one of the main reasons those lines were drawn the way they were. do u think they're monitoring my workstation specifically to make sure i don't mention the specific clause regarding the strait logistics?",
